Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:09.73,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:20.37,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.49,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:06.97,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.97,0:01:14.27,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:20.94,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:28.43,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:59.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know they say,\N"there's no place like home"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:00.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but you're all so comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like some\Nstill have a way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, the young lady with\Nthe charming new hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Roatreamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, this bed seems\Nto be a little lopsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:33.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not just your imagination, milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can put up with that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it really bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:45.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,It creaks if I move\Njust a little, and that bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:10.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,You fixed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:14.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't thank me\Nfor something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?\NSomething to do with that haircut?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:32.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have we reached our destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:54.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:09.64,Titles,,85,0,0,,{\blur0.6}United Front
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Man, what a piece of junk.\NWhere's the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:27.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the priestesses' ship?\NI imagined something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a secret garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:38.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are sibyllae?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:40.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:43.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Quit socializing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:44.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,This ship has Simoun\Nsibyllae on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:56.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We know. That's why we\Nwent out of our way to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:57.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:01.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you take me to the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:05.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I won't allow\Nsuch disrespect! We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you please... Come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I will show them the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait here, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:33.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Messis. First of all,\Nplease make yourselves at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:37.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Captain.\NBut is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:44.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,The youngsters on board this ship\Njust don't look like they're up to battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:49.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,If battles could be won on the basis\Nof looks alone, I would abide by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:54.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,But the Simoun sibyllae\Nare the mainstay of our nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,That is an undeniable fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:00.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,All sides are watching as we\Nlaunch this historical campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,There will be no room for failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, I believe it is\Nimportant that we trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:11.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:15.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then we've agreed\Nto go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NWe're counting on you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Explain, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're about to form\Na united front with these soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,A united front?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:47.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it seems we'll be joining\Nforces with those men somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,With those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:57.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.84,0:07:01.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're being dragged\Ndown further and further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What'll become of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:08.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, a cramped ship getting\Nmore cramped is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:12.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Some people seem\Nto be enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, for real?\NYou're from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I enlisted as\Nsoon as this war began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:23.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good for you. You're an ally of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then as a reward,\NI'll show you around this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:33.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Uh, you see...\NI shouldn't be touching a sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:40.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We haven't gone to the Spring yet,\Nbut that's the only difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't worry... I'm going\Nto become a woman anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:48.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,T-That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:53.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances,\Na lowly enlisted man like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't dare speak to a priestess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:59.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I told you not\Nto make things so complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:07.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,The last few weeks,\Nenemy attacks have increased...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...leaving us no choice but\Nto fall back from our defense lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:16.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,To keep the enemy from gaining more\Nground, we'll launch an operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:21.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to reclaim this town here,\NUrvel, their apparent target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll go down like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:29.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,First, we'll transport our troops\Nby using the Simoun planes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Transport? Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:36.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll outfit the Simouns with\Nspecial transport armor to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:38.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns will transport soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:43.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,If there were another way, we'd do it.\NCan you try to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:53.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,The soldiers aboard will be deployed\Nto secret posts around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:09:00.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,After which the main battalion\Nwill push forward on my signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll launch a pincer attack\Nand destroy the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What else do you wish us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us. Once you've\Ntransported us, your job is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:18.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,The operation will start the night\Nof the new moon, tomorrow at 2300.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:22.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're all\Nin top form for this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could they do such\Na thing to the Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:35.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this to our divine\Naircraft because I want to either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,No way! Don't you feel\Nbad for the Simouns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, it's so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The other day,\Nwe were flying over the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we saw this huge fish, and I\Nthought, "That looks pretty tasty."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can tell she couldn't\Ncare less about the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way she's just about\Nthrowing herself at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:08.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we might not be that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,When your back's to the wall, there's\Nno time to think of others' feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:18.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,In an ideal world, we'd all\Nlearn to understand each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,...just like those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:43.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see I've been mistaken\Nabout sibyllae all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:49.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I thought sibyllae were holier,\Nthose whom must never be violated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't talk much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you disillusioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:58.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, totally the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:02.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'm talking to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm glad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:14.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:16.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hear you're friendly with a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, his name is Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep your standing in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are priestesses\Nserving Tempus Spatium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Indiscretions should be avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:33.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That kind of talk's\Nso behind the times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't help it. I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, I said you\Nshouldn't say things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll all go to\Nthe Spring sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then sibylla or soldier won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Jeez, I'll just quit being a sibylla then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:51.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then it won't be a problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:30.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still, is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fine. Did I keep you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, Mastiff! You're so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to get close?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:52.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Floe, you and\Nthe others serve Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and are closest to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess. Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,We too harbor\Ndeep religious convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:04.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,But rather than out of love\Nand respect for Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:07.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it's because we couldn't\Ngo on if we didn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you think of\Nthis war we're fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:18.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't like it. But we've\Ngot to fight or we'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about killing people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:33.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then why did you enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:39.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't really explain it,\Nbut everyone else enlisted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:45.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's operation is a campaign\Nto reclaim the city where I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:52.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mornings are very beautiful in Urvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:59.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Especially the view from the top of\Nthe tower in the center of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's beyond compare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:04.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right, Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:19.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Begin the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:51.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, men!\NBy the grace of Tempus Spatium!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,By the grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:21.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll fly as close to the ground as\Npossible. Stay out of enemy sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:27.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are banning Ri Majons till further\Nnotice to avoid damaging facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,After transport, disengage\Ncontainers and retreat northwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:33.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun sibyllae,\Nwe pray for your safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have to say they've become ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:00.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get rid of these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard not to drop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:09.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I just hope Mastiff\Ndoesn't run into any danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon,\Nthat hairstyle of yours is so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll see more of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:21.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, this is a pivotal operation,\Na springboard for future missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.37,0:16:25.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You'll understand soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,So this is a front-line mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're almost at\Nthe drop-off point, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're done already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:26.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty quick operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll undock the containers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:31.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,So you didn't like those things either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:36.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess. It's asking too much to even\Npretend to like such awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Flares. Have they spotted us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:48.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, from the number, we should\Nassume it was a trap from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not good. If so, then those\Nold guys will get ambushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll go support them.\NUnderstood, Aer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:12.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,They set us up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:30.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:50.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, they may be ugly,\Nbut they can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll keep up support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,See that? We've got\Nholy priestesses on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Step it up, guys!
Comment: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:00.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right, Rimone... Keep going...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Fire, Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mastiff... Where's Mastiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, Alty, try to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,We don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:40.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kaim? Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,But, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:47.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see...\NI can see people down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:53.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pull it together. Don't dare bring any\Nmore dishonor to the priestesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, at this rate, they'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Ri Majon. Strike with a Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. But a Ri Majon\Nwould unleash too much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:15.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Will you stand by and\Nlet those men die, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:30.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ri Majon ban is lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, the Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't! If we do,\Nit'll put Mastiff in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:40.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,His city will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we don't, he'll die anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a Ri Majon's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing... It's like ten tanks at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can make it...\NWe can make it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:08.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Target is city plaza,\Nthe enemy command center!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Iron Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:12.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to protect Mastiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,To protect Mastiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:30.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:33.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,They blew up\Nthe enemy command center!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:43.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could they really be\NTempus Spatium sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:44.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Could that be Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:52.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right! The priestesses\Nhave cleared the way for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's show what we're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,This battle... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,They can't be divine aircraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:07.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:15.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mastiff, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:19.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't let children like that\Ntake part in a war anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:22.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,This war is ours to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.86,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:52.10,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:59.14,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:06.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.62,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:24.83,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.84,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:32.78,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:38.72,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:44.26,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:47.69,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:53.36,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:59.59,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.92,0:24:06.59,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:11.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim and Alty have taken off on\Na reconnaissance mission as a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:18.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.43,0:24:19.93,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Sisters
